You are building a profile generator for a developer community platform. 
Your task is to write a program that takes a person's basic information—their first name, last name, age, height, 
and whether they like programming—and combines these details into a single, perfectly formatted introductory sentence.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Input Format

The input consists of five lines, corresponding to the variables you need to store:

The first line contains a string, firstName.

The second line contains a string, lastName.

The third line contains an integer, age.

The fourth line contains a double/float, height (in meters).

The fifth line contains a boolean, likesProgramming (either true or false).

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Constraints

1≤Length of firstName≤50

1≤Length of lastName≤50

1≤age≤120

0.5≤height≤3.0

likesProgramming will exactly match the string true or false in lowercase.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Output Format

Print a single sentence substituting the input values into the following template: 
Hello, my name is [firstName] [lastName]. I am [age] years old, [height] meters tall, and it is [likesProgramming] that I like programming!
